OL,3,CFears over safety at night grow ahead
OL,4,Cof Ramadan after Bristol stabbings
OL,6,FA meeting has been held in Easton
OL,7,Fahead of Ramadan to address concerns
OL,8,Fabout the safety of people at night
OL,9,Ffollowing recent stabbings in Bristol.
OL,11,FCommunity leaders came together with
OL,12,Frepresentatives from Avon & Somerset
OL,13,FPolice and Bristol City Council to
OL,14,Fattend the meeting at Easton Community
OL,15,FCentre on Thursday 7 March.
OL,17,FIt comes as four murder investigations
OL,18,Fhave been launched in East Bristol
OL,19,Fsince June last year.
