OL,3,CFears over safety at night grow ahead
OL,4,Cof Ramadan after Bristol stabbings
OL,6,FMohammed Kaise is a youth worker who
OL,7,Fhas lost a friend to knife crime and
OL,8,Fsays he doesn't feel safe on the
OL,9,Fstreets.
OL,11,FHe said: "You never know what can
OL,12,Fhappen to you, you know, with what's
OL,13,Fgoing on in the last couple of months.
OL,15,F"I do feel in danger all the time.
OL,17,F"It's going to be an ongoing problem.
OL,18,FIf we don't tackle it now, more people
OL,19,Fare going to die."
