OL,6,FSaid Mohamed Burale, Vice-Chair of
OL,7,FBristol Somali Forum, was one of those
OL,8,Fwho attended.
OL,10,FHe said: "There is always a worry
OL,11,Fabout the knife crime, it can happen
OL,12,Fto anyone.
OL,14,F"As a community leader, as a father, a
OL,15,Fparent and as a member of the
OL,16,Fcommunity we have concern about what's
OL,17,Fgoing and where can we get help."
