OL,3,CFears over safety at night grow ahead
OL,4,Cof Ramadan after Bristol stabbings
OL,6,FAccording to the Office for National
OL,7,FStatistics a black person is four
OL,8,Ftimes more likely to die from knife
OL,9,Fcrime than a white person.
OL,11,F"Young people are losing their lives,
OL,12,Fothers are going to prison, week in,
OL,13,Fweek out - and it worries everyone",
OL,14,Fsaid Mohamed.
OL,16,FSuperintendent Mark Runacres, from
OL,17,FAvon and Somerset Police, said the
OL,18,Fforce is working with Muslim
OL,19,Fcommunities to understand concerns.
