OL,3,CFears over safety at night grow ahead
OL,4,Cof Ramadan after Bristol stabbings
OL,6,FHe said: "It's a really important time
OL,7,Fof year for the Muslim community, we
OL,8,Funderstand that, lots of people coming
OL,9,Ftogether particularly late in the
OL,10,Fevenings, large numbers in those
OL,11,Flocalities around the mosques.
OL,13,F"We want to engage with those people,
OL,14,Fmake them feel connected with the
OL,15,Fpolice, reassured and safe."
OL,17,FMohammed says it will take a combined
OL,18,Fapproach to address the issue.
